for-ios\/poialongrouteexample","title":"POI Along a Route","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/POIAlongRouteExample"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/GeoJSON":{"abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/GeoJSON","type":"topic","title":"Working with GeoJSON Data","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/geojson","kind":"article","role":"article"}}}